went.

00:29:11.550 --> 00:29:17.910
Now, how Shri Krishna’s advent changed it.

00:29:17.910 --> 00:29:28.940
When Shri Krishna came on this Earth, He said
this is all a leela, it is just a play.

00:29:28.940 --> 00:29:33.930
